E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Faggot - always thinking of interior decoration. Just get job done.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~死基佬，就惦记着室内装修了。赶紧干活。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Sounds real tough for you, tough guy.
~z~Chill, man. I'm just trying to converse with you. My job is hospitality and...
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~冷静，哥们。我就是想跟你聊聊。我的工作是打理夜店和...

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Can you tell me what the plan is?
~z~Fuck you. You are hard work. Don't even know what you are.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~操你妈的，你才硬骨头。撒泡尿照照自己吧。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~We go above Star Junction. High as you can go.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我们要到星汇广场上空，有多高飞多高。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Good. Great. Total fucking silence from here on in.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~好啊，太棒了。现在开始谁都别说话。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Glad you enjoy yourself. I knew you had it in you.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~很高兴你玩得开心。就知道你也嗜血。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~If you buy this team, you gonna have to get a new office.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~要是买下了球队，记得换个新办公室。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Your boss upset a lot of people.
~z~I would do but there is chance Ashvilli's people come for my family back in old place.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我不上是因为Ashvilli可能派人报复我老家的家人。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You want me to shut up? Good.
~z~Only when I hurt people. When I kill them, no, but hurt them, yes, very tense.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~没打死人我就紧张。打死了没事，没打死就会很紧张。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Mr. Ray wanted me to keep watch on you. Make sure you do what told.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~Ray先生让我来盯着你。确保你奉命行事。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Stay the fuck away from Tony, man. You touch him I'll fucking kill you.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你他妈离Tony远点，哥们。敢动他，老子宰了你。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~This is why you tell Mr. Ray you are not "contract killer"? You scared?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~所以你才跟Ray先生说自己不是「契约杀手」？你怕了？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Okay, boy. You love fag man. You like him fuck you?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~好吧，小子。你爱那个基佬。你喜欢被他操？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Fuck, bro, in the future, can we just listen to the radio on these trips.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~操，兄弟，以后咱出来，能不能听听收音机就得了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Yeah. Helps you chill, does it? You get tense?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~是吗，让你放松了是吧？你紧张了？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You ain't getting a peep outta me.
~z~I'm not scared, bro, I just don't like it that's all.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我没怕，兄弟。我就是不喜欢而已，就这样。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Just what I always wanted. A hotline to a fucking charmer.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我可太喜欢了，跟你这个骚逼的聊天专线。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~I didn't want to talk to you in first place.
~z~When you get in building I will give instructions through headset.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~等你进去了，我会用耳机给你下达指令。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You need some people kills, bro. You're sorely lacking right now.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你得练练交流，兄弟。你太缺沟通能力了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~What am I supposed to do anyway?
~z~We must go up high above Star Junction.
~z~You kill Ashvilli, send message and leave building. I pick you up on ground.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你杀掉Ashvilli，给我消息，然后离开大楼。我在地上接应你。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Maybe you right. In the moment you forget everything else, but then they turn into psychos.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~也许是吧。爽的时候是真的爽，之后就成疯婆娘了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Can we just not talk? Is that a problem? Can you shut the fuck up?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~咱能不能不聊了？这样没问题吧？你他妈能不能闭嘴？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Go in, find Ashvilli, kill him. I wait outside with other headset.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~进去，找到Ashvilli，杀了他。我戴着耳机在外面等你。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You gotta remind me why I'm doing this.
~z~You want I should do it? You got money?
~z~You with us now. I thought you done with him. You kill him and take over.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你现在跟着我们，我还以为你已经和他决裂了。把他杀了，取而代之。
~z~暴怒队的办公室在那栋楼里。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~We nearly here. When you go I will take controls.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~差不多到了。你走了我来开飞机。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~I thought it was the fucking cops.
~z~Hey Timmy, I wouldn't have picked you for a musician, bro.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~嘿，Timmy。没想到你还玩音乐啊，兄弟。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Okay, you soon need jump. I will fly chopper.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~好了，你准备跳伞，我来开飞机。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You think they would not notice chopper landing on building? You must go in silent.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~顶楼降落是怕他们没长眼睛吗？你必须潜入进去。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Tell me why we can't just land on the building.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我们就不能直接降落到楼顶吗？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Chill out, bro. I'm lucky to still be alive.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~别急啊，兄弟。还活着就挺好了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~There is building where Rampage Office is.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~这栋楼里就是暴怒队的办公室。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Hey, I know who I am. Sure, I do bad shit, but that ain't who I'm going to be forever.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~喂，我知道自己是什么人。我是干过坏事，但不可能永远干坏事。
~z~我？哈哈。娘们啊，兄弟。我可是多米尼加人。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~When you going to kill fag man your boss?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你什么时候杀那个基佬，你的主子？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You killer like me. That what Bulgarin want you to do, so that what you do.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你和我一样是杀手。既然Bulgarin让你这么做，那你必须这么做。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~We must pick up chopper. Go to heliport.
~z~What's the point in learning English if you gonna be such a miserable asshole?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~嘴里吐不出好话，那你学英语干啥呢？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Ashvilli office is in MeTV Building. You no going to get in from ground so you come in from above.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~Ashvilli的办公室在MeTV大楼里。地面上你是进不去的，只能从上面进去了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Why the fuck did I get involved with these Russians?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我他妈怎么跟这帮毛子搅和上了？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You going to splat if you no pull cord soon.
~z~Here, I have headset for you. This is so we communicate when you in building.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~给，戴上这只耳机。进去以后我们用它联系。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~You're missing out on all the fun here, Timur.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~这么有趣的地方，可惜你不在，Timur。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~It means I don't like doing anything that could easily kill me, but sometimes you got to.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~就是说容易出人命的事我都不喜欢，但有时候不得不干。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Sure, they open up when you shoot in their head. You put people in the ground, my friend.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~确实，一枪爆头就能让他们放开来了。你会把人放倒，我的朋友。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~We go to heliport in Fishmarket South.
~z~Having fun, bro. You should come join me.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~玩得正嗨呢，兄弟。你应该一起来的。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Guess someone else had better take this guy out then.
~z~And you ain't worried about my family?
~z~I'm still in here cutting through these assholes. I tell you when I'm done!
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我还在大杀四方呢。完事了会告诉你的！

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Timur, bro, I like to think I can talk to people. I try to put them at ease, make 'em open up.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~Timur，兄弟，我经常觉得自己很会聊天。让对方放松，放开来说话。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~I mean it, bro. Stay the fuck away from him.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我说了，兄弟，你他妈离他远点。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~I wait for you to kill this asshole.
~z~Here is a headset. I will tell you what you must be doing with it when you're inside.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~戴好这只耳机。进去以后我会通过它指挥你。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Shit, it don't look like I'm gonna be able to do this.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~妈的，看来我没法进去杀人了。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~I ain't killing him, man. What gave you that impression?
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~我不会杀他的，哥们。你怎么会这么想？

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Hey I'm sorry to break up your party, man. You looked like you were having fun.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~喂，抱歉打扰你们狂欢了，哥们。你刚才好像挺开心的。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~How you manage to miss that big building?
~z~Your job is kill Marki Ashvilli for Ray Bulgarin.
E2BG2AU.translated: ~z~你的工作是帮Ray Bulgarin杀了Marki Ashvilli。

E2BG2AU.original: ~z~Marki! Where the fuck are you, man?
